<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 06:10:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和以色列国防军高层就加沙停火展开斗争，同时与真主党展开全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-top-brass-fight-over-gaza-truce-while-spiraling-towards-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-1d17-d231-a1b2-fd5fbd450000</link><description>周六八名以色列国防军士兵的死亡表明，面对哈马斯的适应性策略是困难的，哈马斯将其转变为松散的游击队组织 ■ 内塔尼亚胡继续推销“全面胜利”，再次委托其他人传递坏消息</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-top-brass-fight-over-gaza-truce-while-spiraling-towards-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-1d17-d231-a1b2-fd5fbd450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布在加沙北部和拉法爆炸中丧生的士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-live/eight-idf-soldiers-killed-in-rafah-blast-idf-soldier-dies-from-combat-wounds-in-gaza/00000190-1ea9-d880-a7f5-befd4ae80000</link><description>两名预备役军人在加沙北部的坦克爆炸中丧生；以色列国防军公布了在拉法装甲运兵车爆炸中丧生的 5 名士兵的姓名 ■ 空军袭击南部真主党目标 ■ 报告：美国担心以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击正在为以色列国防军“为全面进攻做准备” ■ 白宫国家安全顾问预计“行动缓慢”未来几天与哈马斯的停火谈判将取得进展 以色列国防部长将访问五角大楼</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 02:36:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-live/eight-idf-soldiers-killed-in-rafah-blast-idf-soldier-dies-from-combat-wounds-in-gaza/00000190-1ea9-d880-a7f5-befd4ae80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，一名以色列士兵周一在拉法受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-rafah-on-monday-idf-announces/00000190-1da3-df11-a3b9-bda7264e0000</link><description>吉瓦蒂旅 19 岁的亚伊尔·罗特曼 (Yair Roitman) 中士在位于拉法东部沙布拉 (Shabura) 街区的一名哈马斯特工的房屋发生爆炸后受伤，该房屋内设了诱杀装置。罗特曼留下了他的父母和五个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 01:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-rafah-on-monday-idf-announces/00000190-1da3-df11-a3b9-bda7264e0000</guid></item><item><title>八名以色列士兵在拉法爆炸中丧生；以色列国防军士兵因早些时候在加沙的战斗受伤而死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-live/g7-leaders-express-concern-about-consequences-of-israels-ongoing-operation-in-rafah/00000190-1988-df11-a3b9-b98f9a730000</link><description>来自黎巴嫩的无人机在以色列北部坠毁，引发大火 ■ 军方表示，火箭袭击了以色列北部的以色列国防军基地附近，但没有造成任何损失的报告 ■ 报告：美国担心以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击正在为以色列国防军“为全面进攻做准备” 白宫国家安全顾问预计未来几天与哈马斯的停火谈判进展“缓慢” 以色列国防部长将访问五角大楼</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 20:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-live/g7-leaders-express-concern-about-consequences-of-israels-ongoing-operation-in-rafah/00000190-1988-df11-a3b9-b98f9a730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 253 天：以色列军队称加沙南部爆炸造成 8 名士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-253-israeli-army-says-eight-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gaza/00000190-1ce1-d3e6-a191-5eeb9d990000</link><description>八名以色列国防军士兵在拉法附近丧生 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹落在以色列北部的以色列国防军基地附近，没有人员伤亡或财产损失 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的无人机坠落在西加利利，引发火灾 ■ 哥伦比亚广播公司新闻报道，一些美国官员认为以色列正在“准备对黎巴嫩更深处的打击”全面进攻的战场” ■ 战争进入 253 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 17:25:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-253-israeli-army-says-eight-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gaza/00000190-1ce1-d3e6-a191-5eeb9d990000</guid></item><item><title>数万以色列人抗议内塔尼亚胡联盟，呼吁达成加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/end-the-war-free-the-hostages-israelis-protest-netanyahu-coalition-call-for-gaza-deal/00000190-1c83-df11-a3b9-bd877d3e0000</link><description>代表加沙人质家属的一个组织发表声明说，“战争每多一天，以色列的利益就会受到损害”，这一点已经非常清楚了。警方发言人称，特拉维夫反政府抗议活动中有 12 人被捕</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 16:37:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/end-the-war-free-the-hostages-israelis-protest-netanyahu-coalition-call-for-gaza-deal/00000190-1c83-df11-a3b9-bd877d3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军证实，八名以色列士兵在加沙南部拉法爆炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gazas-rafah-idf-announces/00000190-1caa-d4b4-a7d6-dcfa04f30000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人丹尼尔·哈加里（Daniel Hagari）表示，装甲运兵车的爆炸可能是由于航母附近放置的爆炸装置或向航母发射的反坦克导弹引起的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 16:13:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gazas-rafah-idf-announces/00000190-1caa-d4b4-a7d6-dcfa04f30000</guid></item><item><title>“10月7日之后，中国的反犹太主义达到了最令人震惊的程度”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-october-7-antisemitism-in-china-reached-the-most-shocking-levels/00000190-19da-dee3-af9b-dfdb33a00000</link><description>中国文化专家尤瓦尔·温雷布 (Yuval Weinreb) 解释了社交媒体在中国的运作方式以及哈马斯袭击后网上发生的情况</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 04:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-october-7-antisemitism-in-china-reached-the-most-shocking-levels/00000190-19da-dee3-af9b-dfdb33a00000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫的一个郊区屈服于东正教的悄然接管。然后自由派联合起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-tel-aviv-suburb-gave-in-to-a-creeping-orthodox-takeover-then-the-liberals-joined-forces/00000190-1994-d880-a7f5-bdd491810000</link><description>当中左翼联手建立统一战线来对抗城市的宗教政客时，会发生什么？一次特别甜蜜的选举胜利的故事</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 03:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-tel-aviv-suburb-gave-in-to-a-creeping-orthodox-takeover-then-the-liberals-joined-forces/00000190-1994-d880-a7f5-bdd491810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，第 252 天：真主党向以色列北部发射数十枚火箭，毁坏房屋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-252-hezbollah-fires-dozens-of-rockets-on-north-israel-damaging-homes/00000190-17a4-df11-a3b9-b7a7d79c0000</link><description>真主党向以色列北部发射数十枚火箭弹和无人机 ■ 哈马斯官员向 CNN 表示：“没有人知道”加沙地带还有多少人质 ■ 以色列官员：如果哈马斯不撤回改变，以色列将不会派代表团参加停火谈判拜登的提议 ■ 以色列士兵在约旦河西岸撞击事件中受伤 ■ 战争进入 252 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-252-hezbollah-fires-dozens-of-rockets-on-north-israel-damaging-homes/00000190-17a4-df11-a3b9-b7a7d79c0000</guid></item><item><title>连环犯罪分子统治着以色列。这就是崩溃开始的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/serial-criminals-rule-israel-thats-where-the-collapse-begins/00000190-1744-d4b4-a7d6-dff63e140000</link><description>以色列不再有真正的国家审计长、国家检察官、公务员委员会或司法部负责调查警察不当行为。内塔尼亚胡的影响力无处不在</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/serial-criminals-rule-israel-thats-where-the-collapse-begins/00000190-1744-d4b4-a7d6-dff63e140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官：本-格维尔涉嫌干预警察工作“严重违反法律”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/state-attorney-ben-gvirs-intervention-in-police-work-gross-violation-of-the-law/00000190-1719-de97-a3d1-ff1f06ce0000</link><description>国家检察官办公室要求高等法院在反对一项将警察置于极右翼国家安全部长之下的法案的请愿书中包括警察局长给总检察长的信，其中详细说明了本格维尔如何绕过他以阻止警察确保加沙援助车队的安全</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 15:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/state-attorney-ben-gvirs-intervention-in-police-work-gross-violation-of-the-law/00000190-1719-de97-a3d1-ff1f06ce0000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争，以色列将把储备税延长一年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-set-to-extend-reserve-duty-by-a-year-due-to-gaza-war/00000190-16fa-de97-a3d1-fffe066b0000</link><description>以色列政府将把预备役军人豁免年龄提高一年的临时命令再延长六个月。发给部长们的解释称，由于战争中伤亡人数“非常大”，以色列国防军仍然需要“大量”人力</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 15:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-set-to-extend-reserve-duty-by-a-year-due-to-gaza-war/00000190-16fa-de97-a3d1-fffe066b0000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长加兰特表示，以色列不会与法国合作缓和黎巴嫩边境与真主党的紧张关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/gallant-israel-wont-work-with-france-to-defuse-tensions-with-hezbollah-on-lebanon-border/00000190-16ff-d4b4-a7d6-deffd2070000</link><description>格兰特指责法国对以色列采取“敌对政策”，同时无视“哈马斯犯下的暴行”。以色列外交部：加兰特的言论“不正确且不恰当”。法国：“对以色列当局的不同声明感到惊讶”</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/gallant-israel-wont-work-with-france-to-defuse-tensions-with-hezbollah-on-lebanon-border/00000190-16ff-d4b4-a7d6-deffd2070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列狙击手在一小时内杀死了杰宁难民营的七名旁观者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-a-single-hour-israeli-snipers-killed-seven-bystanders-at-the-jenin-refugee-camp/00000190-16fe-d231-a1b2-f6ff7d4e0000</link><description>杰宁最近经历了很多艰难的日子，但 5 月 21 日的日子比这一切都更糟。发生了什么？</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:25:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-a-single-hour-israeli-snipers-killed-seven-bystanders-at-the-jenin-refugee-camp/00000190-16fe-d231-a1b2-f6ff7d4e0000</guid></item><item><title>美国对袭击加沙援助车队的以色列右翼组织实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/u-s-to-impose-sanctions-on-right-wing-israeli-group-that-attacked-gaza-aid-convoys/00000190-1715-df11-a3b9-b717136d0000</link><description>制裁针对的是 Tsav 9，该组织与约旦河西岸的以色列预备役军人和犹太定居者有联系，其活动包括拦截、骚扰和破坏援助物资</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:17:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/u-s-to-impose-sanctions-on-right-wing-israeli-group-that-attacked-gaza-aid-convoys/00000190-1715-df11-a3b9-b717136d0000</guid></item><item><title>法院下令释放八个月后在反战示威中被捕的阿拉伯裔以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-release-of-arab-israeli-arrested-in-anti-war-demonstration-after-eight-months/00000190-1699-d529-adb2-37ddb57d0000</link><description>穆罕默德·贾巴林 (Mohammad Jabarin) 于 10 月被捕，被指控与恐怖组织有关联，并在领导反对加沙战争的抗议者后煽动恐怖主义。法官写道，她担心的是，如果罪名成立，他的服刑时间将超过监禁时间</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 13:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-release-of-arab-israeli-arrested-in-anti-war-demonstration-after-eight-months/00000190-1699-d529-adb2-37ddb57d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国在加沙建造的码头面临最新挑战：联合国是否会继续提供援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/latest-challenge-facing-u-s-built-pier-in-gaza-is-whether-the-un-will-keep-delivering-aid/00000190-1695-d621-abfa-5fb535af0000</link><description>以色列的救援行动造成数百名巴勒斯坦人死亡，以色列军队逃离加沙海岸的援助中心，在此之后，联合国正在重新考虑是否可以在不违反核心人道主义原则和危及援助人员安全的情况下利用该项目</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 12:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/latest-challenge-facing-u-s-built-pier-in-gaza-is-whether-the-un-will-keep-delivering-aid/00000190-1695-d621-abfa-5fb535af0000</guid></item><item><title>马克龙表示法国、美国和以色列同意推动路线图以阻止真主党-以色列升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/macron-says-france-u-s-israel-agree-to-push-roadmap-to-stop-hezbollah-israel-escalation/00000190-1677-da3b-a1f1-57f70ee50000</link><description>法国和美国已向以色列和真主党提交了旨在缓解以色列与黎巴嫩边境紧张局势的提案。真主党排除了在以色列和加沙哈马斯停火之前结束敌对行动的可能性</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:28:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/macron-says-france-u-s-israel-agree-to-push-roadmap-to-stop-hezbollah-israel-escalation/00000190-1677-da3b-a1f1-57f70ee50000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨：以色列知道比巴斯一家的命运，将在适当的时候告知公众</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/gantz-israel-knows-fate-of-the-bibas-family-will-inform-public-at-the-appropriate-time/00000190-15fb-d529-adb2-37ff9ca40000</link><description>反对派议员本尼·甘茨在接受电视采访时表示，以色列对加沙地带的活人质人数有“几近确定”的估计，并指责内塔尼亚胡出于政治原因推迟达成协议。比巴斯家族称甘茨言论不负责任</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:42:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/gantz-israel-knows-fate-of-the-bibas-family-will-inform-public-at-the-appropriate-time/00000190-15fb-d529-adb2-37ff9ca40000</guid></item></channel></rss>